Blue-Green Deployment = zero-downtime traffic switch.

Xero Time = time tracking tool.

Xero Time Deployment Types = rolling, blue-green, canary.

Cordon Node = prevents new pod scheduling.

Drain the Blue = safely removes running workloads.

AWS SSM = manage servers without SSH.

Data Source = reads existing infrastructure.

Blue-Green vs Rolling = instant switch vs gradual update.

Drain Node = moves pods safely.

AWS SSM Use Case = automation and patching.
